lines: Enjoying the festivities, I trust? Indeed, it is a time of celebration, but also a time of reflection. The Rising marks the anniversary of the realm's rebirth, and the selfless sacrifices of those who made it possible.
Please do partake in the revelry, and always remember: to ensure a bright future, we must never forget the past.
Thank you again for your help. Even with the bugs vanquished, I would find no joy in our celebration had it cost the wandering minstrel his life.
But let us not worry ourselves with things that will never be. Please do partake in the revelry, and always remember: to ensure a bright future, we must never forget the past.
